# Top-level navigation order (mkdocs-awesome-pages-plugin).
# The spec is the product, so it sits at the very top; everything explanatory
# is grouped under a single "Concepts" section beneath it. 404.md is kept out
# of the nav via `not_in_nav` in mkdocs.yml.
nav:
  - index.md
  - spec
  - Concepts:
      - architecture.md
      - signaling.md
      - encryption-keying.md
      - media-srtp.md
      - transport-noise.md
      - ice-and-relays.md
      - codec
      - keying
      - signaling
      - transport
      - reconstruction.md
      - roadmap.md
      - methodology
      - techniques
      - decisions
      - faq.md
      - legal-and-ethics.md
      - attribution.md
